Now I am told by many that it has no effect on the mob at all!.<br>
I should like to hear the views of other warriors on this so I may make better equipment choices.<br>
<br>
Phaedrax Armourax <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jarkellraven>JarkellRaven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed of Bristlebane</span><br>  Posts: 1571<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/23/02 3:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=151.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charisma And Agro</span><hr size=1> A lot of us have heard this rumor... however there is no evidence whatsoever to back this up.<br>
