<br>
I once accidentally charisma buffed my pet instead of myself and until it wore off, no monsters would touch him (this was in CC).  <br>
Before and after the charisma buff, when I pulled the monsters would happily stop running after me and fight him instead when he ran to my rescue, whilst he had the charisma buff they would keep on after me.  <br>
This was with the same monsters, same pulling techniques, same everything except for the charisma buff.<br>
<br>
Telorea<br>
